Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘…不要叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要带你去散步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你不要闹了 这只笨狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心就要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.58,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}【思い立ったが吉日】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.58,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(35,35)}日本谚语，意指下定决心之时即为最好的行事时机。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天不从人愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.65,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}【月に叢雲、花に風】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.65,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(35,35)}明月为积云遮蔽，花儿飘零于风中；日本谚语，比喻好事多磨。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅 诺诺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我想我应该没见过神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}如果神也有愿望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}会对什么许愿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}就算每天怀着心愿仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}也不知道流星会在何时陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}因此 所谓“对流星许愿就一定会实现心愿”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}其实是难以达成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是 我的愿望一定能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}因为我 正等待着这颗流星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然离家出走 我是个傻孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上有点咸的味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往图书馆的那条蜿蜒曲折的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏着初霜的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小溪的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我全都很喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于走到这步了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺一定要成为宇宙驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:26.39,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞跃巅峰2！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:43.91,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一话  请让我叫你姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又败给重力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时薪720元乘以6小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再减掉今天打破的5个盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦工作一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算算…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才220元而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛顿那老家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来的苹果会由诺诺接住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否当作没有重力这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个苹果 150元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 今天的薪水只剩70元了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天打破盘子、打破平底锅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周居然连冰箱都遭殃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱一般是不会裂开的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有分裂东西特别在行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要回乡下劈柴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想那么快就想不开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你年纪小不懂世事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营业用的冰箱很贵吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概还要再做个半年的白工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再追寻那些不切实际的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心做好你的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包吃包住又包睡的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的地方可没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 诺诺的梦想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙驾驶员～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有地板没打扫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让宇宙驾驶员打扫地板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 您别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺 你还在想着那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要当宇宙驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您以前去过宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是修学旅行去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只是观光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比不上真正的宇宙驾驶员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会当真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是队长年轻的时候是宇宙军候补军人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是炮科退伍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很想当驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您一定要指导我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…首先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读完宇宙高中或宇宙预备科练习学校之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再进入宇宙士官学校至少读四年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过宇宙候补生考试后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再取得宇宙训练中心的38种宇宙兵器装备的资格认证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要再花个六至七年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还要执行二年以上的现场勤务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得长官推荐书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过三次的最终选拔考试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部通过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能前往宇宙舰队执勤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是第一年只能待在练习舰上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少也要花十五年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值得花那么长时间去做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是会打破盘子就能当上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 那边要打蜡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十五年…要花十五年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用每天打破的盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定都能堆起一座梦想之岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处埋着平底锅和冰箱的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请称呼那座岛为“诺诺岛”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会被我埋下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是得靠努力与毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要当好老婆的话 现在马上就可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚之后蜡罐的盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由老公来帮你打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后抱着你到床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微克制一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以这么做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行舰队勤务的那些人 可不懂这些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手…不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里… 惟独那里请放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好玩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 你这样我会很难为的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}我的店会被盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}学长 学长 下一个换我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}等等啦 我还没玩够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}客人 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless… 那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那位客人是何方神圣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是真正的宇宙驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 请等等我——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}请插入通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}请插入通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是刚才那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺非常感激
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到困难就要互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺在姐姐遭遇危机时也定会出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的姐姐是指谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你是宇宙驾驶员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看过这身制服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊 真是让人热血沸腾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自治互助会的宇宙怪兽迎击部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.33,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【自治互助会】（Fraternity）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.33,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(36,35)}由Topless能力者自发建立的组织；Fraternity有“同好会”、“交友会”的含义。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙怪兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊 真是让人热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沸腾到爆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我是姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是对抗宇宙怪兽的正义组织吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保护大家的正义使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:12:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺也想跟姐姐一样 成为宇宙驾驶员保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺诺想成为诺诺莉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺莉莉她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道她是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 你是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会靠努力与毅力加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要那些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够与我并肩作战的 只有成为Topless的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.17,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\an8\fad(200,500)}＊Topless另有“袒胸”的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔克公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对久违的陆地有何感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽到了下下签
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又冷 空气又稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有股奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且连一只海鸟都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有鸟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找的东西 搞不好根本就没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的预测是莎贝坦双胞胎做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们最近的精确度下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 终于说出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次我也有预测到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大声嚷嚷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才航路安全局也发布了发现可疑陨石坠落的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问 宇宙怪兽就在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是抽中上上签了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 本月的击坠数 又是公主稳拿第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和优等生没得比呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连个避难警报都没发布不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺 你不回店里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘放不下心 正开车到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是对不起 我没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刚才通报的那个东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一大把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我向你老婆告状哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火…火星人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着将其捕获 掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从左右包抄 行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是什么怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是宇宙怪兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新种类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.07,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}【dix-neuf】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.07,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(35,35)}法语数字19
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.87,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine·dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是宇宙怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制伏它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是阻止它而已 都不能独自应付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会妨碍我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Physical Canceller 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.65,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}【Physical Canceller】
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.65,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(47,35)}物理消除器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exotic Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.68,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}【Exotic Maneuver】
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.68,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(47,35)}特异机动操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 以太在闪光吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.87,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,800)}【以太】（ether）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.87,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,800)\pos(38,35)}一种曾被假想的、充满整个宇宙的电磁波传播媒质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明跟她说过会碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到的 诺诺 挪不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是诺诺莉莉的话 就绝不会放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认清现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上总有办不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙怪兽就要醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…一定会救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你出来 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宇宙去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 如果是诺诺莉莉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让它逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:35.03,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系 第4行星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Buster
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}Gaiter
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:55.20,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【Gaiter】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:55.20,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(47,35)}绑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf 你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么犹豫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐被…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电踢——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Buster
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.66,0:24:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Beam
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.66,0:24:21.82,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【Beam】
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.66,0:24:21.82,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(47,35)}光束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.81,0:24:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.55,0:24:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺也变成“Topless”了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.59,0:24:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.64,0:26:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了火星危机的诺诺和姐姐的Topless搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.18,0:26:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却被宇宙军队逮捕 还被铐上了手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.75,0:27:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此时 发生了撼动卫星基地的重力震反应
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.32,0:27:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙怪兽又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.39,0:27:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞跃巅峰2！ 下集
